{"tid":560891,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[熱烈地彈琴系列] 周嘉儀情人節宣佈分手","createTime":"2018-02-14T13:34:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T03:25:55.000Z","uid":38456,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6aef296f60760f79dc9f71aed844aab825baccb2","tid":560891,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T13:34:48.000Z","msg":"今日係情人節，周嘉儀如常喺fb同fans玩互動，佢貼咗幾張著住紅色背心裙嘅相兼留言話：「各位早晨，今日係2月14號星期三。今日部份時間有陽光，夜晚沿岸有霧，都幾溫暖，15至19度。正所謂女為悅己者容，不過+2(嘉儀)就覺得扮靚啲可以令自己開心啲醒神啲，唔需要係為任何人嘅，+2(嘉儀)喺度祝各位無論有情人定冇情人都快快樂樂，開開心心過每一日。今晚我就同一大班朋友一齊食團年飯喇，你哋呢？」"},{"pid":"ebfeb29632b8de4013ff4cacb3fa9128b688a981","tid":560891,"uid":38456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T13:41:42.000Z","msg":"比人隨插即棄"},{"pid":"0f6a9d76bbd475934778de5e64e652fad3572ecb","tid":560891,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T13:54:48.000Z","msg":"佢條仔係邊個？"},{"pid":"c8208fbdf223da7a5801cd7e3780dedf1bff07a9","tid":560891,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:00:31.000Z","msg":"大陸"},{"pid":"344c0860ceb6eaeffd1b4547a002f4267a1f36ba","tid":560891,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"分手？"},{"pid":"35a4c9e4f4712865c1f84fda3f362ef8de985389","tid":560891,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"344c0860ceb6eaeffd1b4547a002f4267a1f36ba","tid":560891,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T14:48:28.000Z","msg":"分手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:19:19.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"33532c94ace27bb1c4e8a0d54fb0b4ef1b9daa8f","tid":560891,"uid":106247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T01:37:00.000Z","msg":"各位巴打又有機會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628bb73ec5b7f65286d466eb0b4897db04623162","tid":560891,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33532c94ace27bb1c4e8a0d54fb0b4ef1b9daa8